description: BLUE RIBBON SEASONAL LOWFAT ICE CREAM VANILLA 2 LTR 1 TUB CASE  6 TUBSTreat the family with Blue Ribbon Classic Vanilla for dessert Made with buttermilk and creamy vanilla it is perfect for any family It is the Australias 1 Vanilla frozen dessert Discover why Blue Ribbon has been famously running out since forever and why it doesnt last long in the freezer There is a tub or flavour of Blue Ribbon for everyone in the family to create happy memories together   Blue Ribbon was created by Edwin Ted Streets in 1968 in the small town of Corrimal NSW He began by selling his signature buttermilk vanilla ice cream to his neighbours thanks to his wife Daisy and his brothers and today Streets has become one of Australias biggest and best known ice cream makers From humble beginnings Blue Ribbon has come to be Australias favourite vanilla and now includes some of your favourite frozen dessert flavours like chocolate Neapolitan cookies  cream to name a few   Blue Ribbon is loved by Australians and is proudly made in Australia   Looking for a serving suggestion Blue Ribbon goes well with saucy toppings or fruit Its also fun to eat in cones during summer for a nostalgic trip back to bring back childhood memories; however we like it the best just the way it isTreat your family and the ones you love with Blue Ribbon Vanilla 2 litre ice cream for dessert or a snackBlue Ribbon icecream has been enjoyed by generations of Australians since 1968A delicious icecream tub the whole family can share made with quality ingredientsFrom the maker of Australias 1 vanilla icecream Blue Ribbon is made in AustraliaFind out why Blue Ribbon icecream tub has famously been running out in Australian freezers since foreverBlue Ribbon frozen dessert icecream tub is made with creamy wholesome buttermilk
